%% Gantt / Timeline — canonical safe pattern per DESIGN.md (iterated from real overflow reports).
%% Brief: Product roadmap. For any .md that will be previewed, inside gantt use ONLY short codes (V1.1 etc.).
%% Full mapping + details = immediate table below. ASCII fallback always included for zero-overflow reliability.
%% Dials: Complexity 3, Density 3, Restraint 9.
%% Gantt specifics: time axis, category sections, short IDs inside bars, table beside, ASCII companion.
gantt
    title Product Roadmap (safe for previewers)
    dateFormat  YYYY-MM-DD
    axisFormat  %m/%d
    section V1 Core
    V1.1                 :a1, 2026-07-01, 6w
    V1.2                 :a2, after a1, 7w
    V1.3                 :a3, after a2, 4w
    section V2 Enhance
    V2.1                 :b1, after a3, 5w
    V2.2                 :b2, after b1, 5w

